        Planning Your 2027 Property Sale in Brisbane: A Practical Timeline
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        If you are planning to sell in 2027, the preparation work starts now. Here is a practical timeline working backwards from your target settlement date.
      </p>
